=== 初期发展阶段 ===
2013年11月，[[二十世纪福斯|二十世纪福斯]]就另一部金刚狼独立电影项目展开谈判，[[詹姆斯·曼高德|詹姆斯·曼高德]]为该片撰寫前期劇本纲要（Treatment），而{{le|蘿倫·舒勒·唐納|Lauren Shuler Donner}}以“The Donner Company”回归制作该片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2013/11/james-mangold-hugh-jackman-sinking-claws-into-another-the-wolverine-film-627461/|title=James Mangold, Hugh Jackman Sinking Claws Into Another ‘The Wolverine’ Film|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2013-11-05|accessdate=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025194438/http://deadline.com/2013/11/james-mangold-hugh-jackman-sinking-claws-into-another-the-wolverine-film-627461/|archive-date=2016-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/12/06/storylines-we-want-to-see-in-wolverine-3|title=STORYLINES WE WANT TO SEE IN WOLVERINE 3|last=Schedeen|first=Jesse|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2013-12-06|accessdate=2016-10-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/wolverine-james-mangold-x-men-1200797970/|title=Hugh Jackman, James Mangold Lining Up for Another ‘Wolverine’ Film|last=Variety Staff|first=|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2013-11-05|accessdate=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113035225/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/wolverine-james-mangold-x-men-1200797970/|archive-date=2016-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/wolverine-sequel-works-james-mangold-653337|title='Wolverine' Sequel in the Works With James Mangold|last=McClintock|first=Pamela|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2013-11-05|accessdate=2016-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113050618/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/wolverine-sequel-works-james-mangold-653337|archive-date=2016-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在那时，休·杰克曼对回归另一部金刚狼电影处于模棱两可的态度<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.scifinow.co.uk/news/the-wolverine-2-hugh-jackman-reveals-cool-ideas-for-script/|title=THE WOLVERINE 2: HUGH JACKMAN REVEALS "COOL IDEAS" FOR SCRIPT|last=Glick|first=Martin|work={{link-en|SciFiNow|SciFiNow}}|date=2013-11-15|accessdate=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113062521/https://www.scifinow.co.uk/news/the-wolverine-2-hugh-jackman-reveals-cool-ideas-for-script/|archive-date=2016-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/hugh-jackman-talks-third-wolverine-solo-movie/|title=Hugh Jackman Talks Up Third Wolverine Solo Movie|last=Plumb|first=Ali|work=[[Empire_Magazine|Empire Magazine]]|date=2013-11-15|accessdate=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310223137/http://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/hugh-jackman-talks-third-wolverine-solo-movie/|archive-date=2016-03-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，虽然杰克曼坚持认为他与福克斯的合同在拍完《[[X战警：逆转未来|X战警：逆转未来]]》（2014年）后需要重新协商<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2013/11/13/hugh-jackman-wolverine-sequel|title=Hugh Jackman on 'The Wolverine' sequel, Neill Blomkamp's 'Chappie,' musicals he's eyeing|last=Beard|first=Lanford|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2013-11-13|accessdate=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161124011513/http://www.ew.com/article/2013/11/13/hugh-jackman-wolverine-sequel|archive-date=2016-11-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并不意味着他会离开该系列，因为他从《X戰警2》（2003年）开始一直以“每次一部”的形式拍该系列电影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://me.ign.com/en/movies/73719/news/jackman-on-wolverine-sequel-it-has-to-be-great|title=JACKMAN ON WOLVERINE SEQUEL: "IT HAS TO BE GREAT"|last=O'Brien|first=Lucy|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2013-11-17|accessdate=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113045742/http://me.ign.com/en/movies/73719/news/jackman-on-wolverine-sequel-it-has-to-be-great|archive-date=2016-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他还談到，「我想和吉姆和[[電影製片|制作人]]蘿倫·舒勒·唐納一起共事，因为我们有非常好的经驗，我真的为《[[金刚狼2|金刚狼2]]》（2013年）感到骄傲。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/the-wolverine-3-sequel-news-hugh-jackman/|title=Hugh Jackman Talks THE WOLVERINE Sequel; Says "There Are Some Really Cool Ideas"|last=Chitwood|first=Adam|work=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|date=2013-11-14|accessdate=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113035131/http://collider.com/the-wolverine-3-sequel-news-hugh-jackman/|archive-date=2016-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该月后期，詹姆斯·曼高德宣布，电影的前期制作和剧本初稿写作方面还没有开始，虽然他进一步表示，“我会说我还没進行到那一步，但我已经開始在『用手指按按鍵了』，我们就这么说吧。我们一直在打字，一直在构思新想法，并与主创人员一直沟通。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/the-wolverine-2-sequel-james-mangold-interview/|title=Director James Mangold Talks Developing THE WOLVERINE for Fox, Depicting Japan in the Film, and the Status of THE WOLVERINE 2|last=Cook|first=Tommy|work=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|date=2013-11-19|accessdate=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113035136/http://collider.com/the-wolverine-2-sequel-james-mangold-interview/|archive-date=2016-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在《金刚狼2》发行后不久，曼高德谈及一部潜在的续集，目的是不将其变成“世界能得救吗？”主题电影，同时也强调“不会拍出同样的电影”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://screenrant.com/wolverine-3-classic-costume-james-mangold-explained/|title=James Mangold Talks Wolverine 3 & Classic Yellow Costume|last=Keyes|first=Rob|work=Screen Rant|date=2013-11-21|accessdate=2016-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113041208/http://screenrant.com/wolverine-3-classic-costume-james-mangold-explained/|archive-date=2016-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/the-wolverine-2-sequel-james-mangold-interview/|title=James Mangold Talks THE WOLVERINE, Making a Different Kind of Superhero Movie, His Action Style, the Editing Process, 3D, and More|last=Weintraub|first=Steve|work=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|date=2013-06-25|accessdate=2016-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113035136/http://collider.com/the-wolverine-2-sequel-james-mangold-interview/|archive-date=2016-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曼高德也提到了他可能用到的一些潜在的故事发展框架，同时也处理以角色为中心的问题<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.unleashthefanboy.com/movies/james-mangold-gives-thoughts-wolverine-3-included-classic-costume/79264|title=James Mangold Gives His Thoughts On WOLVERINE 3|last=M|first=Christopher|work=Unleash The Fanboy|date=2013-11-21|accessdate=2016-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113051349/http://www.unleashthefanboy.com/movies/james-mangold-gives-thoughts-wolverine-3-included-classic-costume/79264|archive-date=2016-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>，“我认为对我来说最重要的是，你听说我如何构造脚本，只是找出关键的关系，它是什么，整部电影的主题是什么，我有一个好的角度，但我还没准备好谈论它！”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/11/20/director-james-mangold-on-the-wolverine-unleashed-unrated-version-and-the-next-wolverine-film|title=DIRECTOR JAMES MANGOLD ON THE WOLVERINE UNLEASHED UNRATED VERSION AND THE NEXT WOLVERINE FILM|last=Goldman|first=Eric|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2013-11-19|accessdate=2016-10-30}}</ref>。2013年12月，杰克曼谈到接近他扮演这个角色的结束，虽然他声明这部电影仍处于初期发展阶段<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2013/12/hugh-jackman-wolverine-interview|title=Hugh Jackman on Why He Shoots Wolverine Dialogue Scenes in the Morning, and What a Nice Guy Rupert Murdoch Is|last=Miller|first=Julie|work=[[Vanity_Fair_(magazine)|Vanity Fair]]|date=2013-12-05|accessdate=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161001103901/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2013/12/hugh-jackman-wolverine-interview|archive-date=2016-10-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。杰克曼还透露，曼高德和他已经开始谈论潜在的想法，他补充表示：“曼高德和我昨晚在电话上谈论了一些想法，但没有剧本和作家，所以一切仍然无法确定。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/12/06/hugh-jackman-says-he-may-not-do-the-next-wolverine-movie|title=HUGH JACKMAN SAYS HE MAY NOT DO THE NEXT WOLVERINE MOVIE|last=Cornet|first=Roth|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2013-12-06|accessdate=2016-10-27}}</ref>

