== 回響 ==

=== 評價 ===
《羅根》凭借出色的演出，导演，剧本和对金刚狼神话史的尊重而獲得了一致好評，甚至有些影評人認為這是至今最佳的《X戰警》電影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/logan-movie-review-roundup/1100-6447990/ |title=Logan Movie Review Roundup |publisher=GameSpot |accessdate=2017-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222031955/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/logan-movie-review-roundup/1100-6447990/ |archive-date=2017-02-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamezone.com/news/review-roundup-logan-is-shaping-up-to-be-the-quintessential-super-hero-film-3451000 |title=Review Roundup: Logan is shaping up to be the quintessential super hero film |publisher=GameZone |accessdate=2017-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219105953/http://www.gamezone.com/news/review-roundup-logan-is-shaping-up-to-be-the-quintessential-super-hero-film-3451000 |archive-date=2017-02-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據427條評論，持有94%的新鮮度，平均得分8.0/10，对该片的综合评价如下，“在一部暴力但深思到令人惊讶的超级英雄动作电影里，休·杰克曼通过其严肃和独特的表演完美的谢幕了“金刚狼”这个不朽角色。”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/logan_2017/ |title=Logan (2017) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2017-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525144014/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/logan_2017/ |archive-date=2017-05-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分77，代表「普遍正面好評」的評價<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/logan-2017 |title=Logan reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2017-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317031223/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/logan-2017 |archive-date=2017-03-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

