box-office-with-80-million-opening/|archive-date=2017-03-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ew.com/movies/2017/03/02/logan-box-office-predictions/?xid=entertainment-weekly_socialflow_twitter|title=Box office preview: Logan to slash competition|author=Joey Nofli|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2017-03-02|accessdate=2017-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305115500/http://ew.com/movies/2017/03/02/logan-box-office-predictions/?xid=entertainment-weekly_socialflow_twitter|archive-date=2017-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而福斯的估計較為保守，預計首週末的收入額約落在6,000萬美元的範圍內<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/film/news/logan-box-office-2017-biggest-debut-1202000089/|title=Box Office: ‘Logan’ Slicing and Dicing Toward Year’s Biggest Debut|author=Brent Lang|work=Variety|date=2017-03-01|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170302101544/http://variety.com/2017/film/news/logan-box-office-2017-biggest-debut-1202000089/|archive-date=2017-03-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該片於星期四的午夜場中進帳950萬美元，與《[[X戰警：天啟|X戰警：天啟]]》（820萬美元）和《[[奇異博士_(電影)|奇異博士]]》（940萬美元）的成績相當<ref>{{cite|title='Logan’ Claws to Strong $9.5 Million at Thursday Box Office|url=http://www.thewrap.com/logan-strong-9-5-million-thursday-box-office/|accessdate=2017-03-03|work=TheWrap|date=2017-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303171650/http://www.thewrap.com/logan-strong-9-5-million-thursday-box-office/|archive-date=2017-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首映週末票房收入為8,841萬美元，位居當週票房冠軍，並成為《金鋼狼》系列電影中最高的首週末成績<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-results-logan-sinks-claws-huge-853m-debut-983259?utm_source=twitter&utm_source=flynxapp.com&utm_medium=referral|title=Weekend Box Office: 'Logan' Sinks Claws Into Huge $85.3M Debut|author=Pamela McClintock|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2017-03-05|accessdate=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306034022/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-results-logan-sinks-claws-huge-853m-debut-983259