自電影製作以來，[[萊恩·雷諾斯|萊恩·雷諾斯]]和傑克曼雙雙承認他們渴望死侍與金鋼狼能一同出現在另一部劇情長片中。《惡棍英雄：死侍》續集的編劇表示，儘管《羅根》是傑克曼飾演金鋼狼的最後一部作品，但兩個演員的慾望增加了其在未來發生的潛力<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movieweb.com/deadpool-2-writers-trilogy-wolverine-crossover/|title=Deadpool 2 Writers Talk Wolverine Crossover and Trilogy Plans|last=Scott|first=Ryan|work=Movieweb|access-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222003705/http://movieweb.com/deadpool-2-writers-trilogy-wolverine-crossover/|archive-date=2017-02-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/799503-ryan-reynolds-eager-for-deadpool-and-wolverine-team-up-movie#/slide/1 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218070029/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/799503-ryan-reynolds-eager-for-deadpool-and-wolverine-team-up-movie#/slide/1 |archive-date=2017-02-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/hugh-jackman-wolverine-may-not-retire-ryan-reynolds-deadpool/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218064848/https://www.cnet.com/news/hugh-jackman-wolverine-may-not-retire-ryan-reynolds-deadpool/ |archive-date=2017-02-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年2月，《金鋼狼：武士之戰》和《羅根》的聯合編劇及導演詹姆斯·曼高德表示，隨著[[X-23|蘿拉·金尼／X-23]]進入X戰警電影世界，他希望看到這個角色出現在未來的電影中，如果成真，他會想以某種形式參與<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.comicbookmovie.com/x-men/logan/logan-director-james-mangold-discusses-working-with-hugh-jackman-a148892 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218063421/https://www.comicbookmovie.com/x-men/logan/logan-director-james-mangold-discusses-working-with-hugh-jackman-a148892 |archive-date=2017-02-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同月，[[派崔克·史都華|派崔克·史都華]]表示，自己將不會在未來的系列電影中繼續飾演X教授一角<ref>[http://ew.com/movies/2017/02/24/patrick-stewart-x-men-retiring/ Patrick Stewart says he's retiring from X-Men franchise: 'I'm done'] {{Wayback|url=http://ew.com/movies/2017/02/24/patrick-stewart-x-men-retiring/ |date=20170225032651 }} Entertainment Weekly, Retrieved February 24, 2017</ref>，但派崔克卻在2022年回歸[[奇異博士2：失控多重宇宙|奇異博士2：失控多重宇宙]]飾演X教授。

